libdaemon: libdaemon - library for Unix daemon programming
libdaemon:
libdaemon: libdaemon is a lightweight C library that eases the writing of
libdaemon: Unix daemons. It consists of a wrapper around fork() which does
libdaemon: the correct daemonization procedure of a process, a wrapper
libdaemon: around syslog() for simpler and compatible log output to Syslog
libdaemon: or stderr, an API for writing PID files, serialization of Unix
libdaemon: signals, etc.
libdaemon:
libdaemon: Packaged by Georgi D. Sotirov <gdsotirov@dir.bg>
